==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Enclitic
<hw>En*clit"ic</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Gram.)</fld> <def>A word which
is joined to another so closely as to lose its proper accent, as the
pronoun <xex>thee</xex> in <xex>prithee</xex> (pray thee).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Enclitically</ent>⟦br⟧
